data.description: Freshly updated home in cozy Miller's Point! Enjoy cooking with granite counter tops. The huge living room with high ceilings has a warm fireplace for you to enjoy this holiday season. 4 spacious bedrooms share 2 completely upgraded bathrooms with custom-tiled showers. Relax in the sunroom or BBQ on the patio. Sleep soundly at night and reap the home insurance discounts with a $20,000 commercial-grade fire sprinkler system. Get the home you deserve. Visit today!
